kin, P.A., Global precipitation: A 17-year monthly analysis based on gauge observations, satellite estimates, and numerical model outputs (1997) Bull. Am. Meteorol. Soc., 78, pp. 2539-2558","Dixon, K.W.; NOAA - Geophys. Fluid Dynam. Lab., Princeton Univ. Forrestal Campus, PO Box 308, Princeton, NJ 08542, United States; email: kd@gfdl.noaa.gov",,,,,,,,09218181,,GPCHE,,"English","Global Planet. Change",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-0038356546
